1) create level and toggle bar
2)create a 3*3 grid
3) apply css colors in the background
4)apply colors based on the mode
5)apply transitions for the grid(fade in and fade out)
6)apply color change for each box in the grid
7)apply transitions for each box
8)generate random numbers (n unique random numbers where n*n is the size of the box)
9)highlight the box basing on those random numbers
10)display the color change for n seconds
11)now user selects the boxes
12)if user selects wrong box then display red color and go to level 0
13)if he selects all colors correctly increment the level
14)if he completes all 10 levels the display congragulations
